name: Monstera Deliciosa
description: Large, glossy leaves with distinctive splits and holes. Perfect statement plant for any room.

name: Fiddle Leaf Fig
description: Elegant tree with large, violin-shaped leaves. Adds height and drama to any space.

name: Snake Plant
description: Hardy, upright leaves with striking patterns. Perfect for beginners and low-light areas.

name: ZZ Plant
description: Glossy, dark green leaves that thrive in low light. Nearly indestructible and perfect for busy people.

name: Pothos
description: Trailing vine with heart-shaped leaves. Easy to care for and perfect for hanging or climbing.

name: Peace Lily
description: Elegant white flowers and glossy leaves. Great for air purification and low-light spaces.

name: Philodendron
description: Heart-shaped leaves that trail beautifully. Fast-growing and easy to propagate.

name: Alocasia
description: Dramatic, arrow-shaped leaves with striking veins. Makes a bold statement in any room.

name: Calathea
description: Beautiful patterned leaves that move throughout the day. Perfect for adding texture and interest.

name: String of Pearls
description: Unique trailing succulent with bead-like leaves. Perfect for hanging baskets and high shelves.

name: Bird of Paradise
description: Tropical plant with large, banana-like leaves. Creates a lush, jungle atmosphere.

name: Chinese Evergreen
description: Colorful, patterned leaves that thrive in low light. Perfect for adding color to dark corners.

name: Spider Plant
description: Arching leaves with plantlets that dangle like spiders. Great for hanging and air purification.

name: Rubber Plant
description: Large, glossy leaves with a tree-like form. Adds height and sophistication to any space.

name: Dracaena
description: Tall, architectural plant with striped leaves. Perfect for adding vertical interest and structure.

name: Pilea Peperomioides
description: Round, coin-like leaves on long stems. Also known as the 'Pancake Plant' for its unique appearance.

name: Tradescantia
description: Colorful, trailing plant with purple and green leaves. Fast-growing and easy to care for.

name: Aglaonema
description: Beautiful, patterned leaves in various colors. Thrives in low light and adds color to any space.

name: Peperomia
description: Compact plants with interesting leaf shapes and textures. Perfect for small spaces and beginners.

name: Begonia
description: Colorful leaves and sometimes flowers. Great for adding bright colors and interesting patterns.
